  <brief_title>Local Anesthetic Infiltration and Infusion for Pain Control After Hip Replacement</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Evaluation of the Efficacy of Local Infiltration Analgesia and Infusion for Total Hip Arthroplasty</official_title>
